1435
01:46:40,398 --> 01:46:42,559
I didn't duck,
and I hardly cried.

1436
01:46:42,634 --> 01:46:46,092
She hit you?

1437
01:46:46,170 --> 01:46:50,163
Well, she did that
to me once too,

1438
01:46:50,241 --> 01:46:53,005
but I think I did cry.

1439
01:46:54,912 --> 01:46:58,871
<i>Mama, I'm sorry
if you're sad.</i>

1440
01:46:58,950 --> 01:47:01,248
Well,

1441
01:47:01,319 --> 01:47:04,413
give me a big kiss then,
and I'll never be sad again.

1442
01:47:11,963 --> 01:47:14,864
And you best not be sad
neither.

1443
01:47:14,932 --> 01:47:18,163
You understand?

