1546
01:55:12,912 --> 01:55:15,904
Hi, honey.
Look what I got you.

1547
01:55:15,982 --> 01:55:18,007
Ah...

1548
01:55:18,084 --> 01:55:21,542
Ed, how sweet!

1549
01:55:21,621 --> 01:55:24,055
Lilies! My favorite. Yeah.

1550
01:55:24,123 --> 01:55:27,251
I know.
Sometimes I even amaze myself.

1551
01:55:27,326 --> 01:55:31,422
What's the occasion?
Oh, honey, I just...

1552
01:55:31,497 --> 01:55:34,466
Feel sorry about
the past few months.

1553
01:55:34,534 --> 01:55:38,527
I don't know what you're really
