her good-bye. Oh, I know.

1626
02:00:21,255 --> 02:00:25,214
These things are difficult, but
she died peacefully in her sleep.

1627
02:00:25,293 --> 02:00:28,558
To tell you the truth, I thought
you'd be happy for Mrs. Threadgoode.

1628
02:00:28,629 --> 02:00:31,655
Happy? Why, yes! This
is what she wanted.

1629
02:00:31,732 --> 02:00:33,666
